Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命征呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除血壓偏低以外還算安定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備交叉配血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
