Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩儀小姐  要剪開和服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出血很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸血包多準備一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…盡頭
