Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教了  干也君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  蒼崎所長
